      * nfsserver       (ocf:heartbeat:nfsserver):    Started &node1;
      * exportfs-nfs    (ocf:heartbeat:exportfs):     Started &node1;
      * vip-nfs         (ocf:heartbeat:IPaddr2):      Started &node1;

